---
title: Crispy Chickpea & Kale Salad with Cucumber, Pickled Shallot & Lemony Tahini Dressing
description: Think kale salad is so 2010s? Not if you make it like we do! Kale is massaged and then coated in a creamy, peppery, tangy tahini-garlic-yogurt-lemon dressing, with crunchy cukes and a tangle of pickled shallots. Then it’s topped with a heap of cumin and paprika-seasoned roasted chickpeas—smashed just a bit to make them extra-crispy. This salad is so now!
